  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unlock the Secrets of Your Subconscious in <i>Skyward Dream</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/4294d5881d67d49539e3ff4e4de10fc9.poster.avif?t=1734600766\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/4294d5881d67d49539e3ff4e4de10fc9.webm?t=1734600766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/4294d5881d67d49539e3ff4e4de10fc9.mp4?t=1734600766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skyward Dream is a first-person platforming adventure where you’ll explore the surreal, interconnected layers of your own mind. As part of a groundbreaking new experiment—the Skyward Dream Project—you’ve chosen to dive deep into your subconscious through an experimental form of therapy. This method promises to unlock your hidden potential, inspire self-discovery, and help you overcome your deepest inner struggles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/769318366e94f0358cd39094e8733889.poster.avif?t=1734600766\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/769318366e94f0358cd39094e8733889.webm?t=1734600766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/769318366e94f0358cd39094e8733889.mp4?t=1734600766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare to journey through a mesmerizing dreamscape where the lines between reality and imagination blur. Each layer of your mind reflects a personal challenge, from fears of transformation to battles with overthinking. You’ll unlock new abilities that mirror your own growth, empowering you to overcome obstacles and dive deeper into the unknown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/cdc1a16a036c1b799eaafbe8cb0ce4fb.poster.avif?t=1734600766\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/cdc1a16a036c1b799eaafbe8cb0ce4fb.webm?t=1734600766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/cdc1a16a036c1b799eaafbe8cb0ce4fb.mp4?t=1734600766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock Powerful Abilities:</strong> As you progress through the dreamscape, gain new abilities that mirror your personal growth and help you overcome the challenges you face within your mind.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore Surreal, Interconnected Environments:</strong> Journey through beautifully crafted dream worlds, each one representing different aspects of your subconscious and inner struggles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uncover Hidden Memories:</strong> Find pages containing your thoughts and memories, buried deep in your mind, and piece together your story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deep, Intriguing Storyline:</strong> Confront your inner demons and uncover the truth behind the mysterious voice guiding you through the Sleep Paralysis stage. Can you escape from the depths of your own mind?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on a deeply personal journey of self-discovery, where every challenge helps you unlock your true potential. With its unique, stylized visuals and immersive gameplay, <i>Skyward Dream</i> offers an atmospheric adventure filled with discovery at every turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to face your inner fears and unlock the power within?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unlock the Secrets of Your Subconscious in <i>Skyward Dream</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/4294d5881d67d49539e3ff4e4de10fc9.poster.avif?t=1734600766\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/4294d5881d67d49539e3ff4e4de10fc9.webm?t=1734600766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/4294d5881d67d49539e3ff4e4de10fc9.mp4?t=1734600766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skyward Dream is a first-person platforming adventure where you’ll explore the surreal, interconnected layers of your own mind. As part of a groundbreaking new experiment—the Skyward Dream Project—you’ve chosen to dive deep into your subconscious through an experimental form of therapy. This method promises to unlock your hidden potential, inspire self-discovery, and help you overcome your deepest inner struggles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/769318366e94f0358cd39094e8733889.poster.avif?t=1734600766\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/769318366e94f0358cd39094e8733889.webm?t=1734600766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/769318366e94f0358cd39094e8733889.mp4?t=1734600766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare to journey through a mesmerizing dreamscape where the lines between reality and imagination blur. Each layer of your mind reflects a personal challenge, from fears of transformation to battles with overthinking. You’ll unlock new abilities that mirror your own growth, empowering you to overcome obstacles and dive deeper into the unknown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/cdc1a16a036c1b799eaafbe8cb0ce4fb.poster.avif?t=1734600766\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/cdc1a16a036c1b799eaafbe8cb0ce4fb.webm?t=1734600766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776230/extras/cdc1a16a036c1b799eaafbe8cb0ce4fb.mp4?t=1734600766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock Powerful Abilities:</strong> As you progress through the dreamscape, gain new abilities that mirror your personal growth and help you overcome the challenges you face within your mind.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore Surreal, Interconnected Environments:</strong> Journey through beautifully crafted dream worlds, each one representing different aspects of your subconscious and inner struggles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uncover Hidden Memories:</strong> Find pages containing your thoughts and memories, buried deep in your mind, and piece together your story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deep, Intriguing Storyline:</strong> Confront your inner demons and uncover the truth behind the mysterious voice guiding you through the Sleep Paralysis stage. Can you escape from the depths of your own mind?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on a deeply personal journey of self-discovery, where every challenge helps you unlock your true potential. With its unique, stylized visuals and immersive gameplay, <i>Skyward Dream</i> offers an atmospheric adventure filled with discovery at every turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to face your inner fears and unlock the power within?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
